                        "name": "hhatfield",
                        "displayName": "H Hatfield",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "One thing you can do in ZF >= 1.11 is use Zend_Http_UserAgent and check to see if the client supports xhtml_file_upload (which none of the iOS devices do, currently).\r\n\r\nCheck out the docs online for how to set it up: http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/manual\/en\/zend.http.user-agent.html",
